create.t.sol
├── when the recipient is the zero address
│  └── it reverts
└── when the recipient is not the zero address
   ├── when the deposit is zero
   │  └── it reverts
   └── when the deposit is not zero
      ├── when the start time is after the stop time
      │  └── it reverts
      ├── when the start time is the same as the stop time
      │  └── it creates the stream
      └── when the start time is before the stop time
        ├── when the token is not a contract
        │  └── it reverts
        ├── when the token misses the return value
        │  └── it creates the stream
        └── when the token is ERC-20 compliant
           ├── it creates the stream
           ├── it bumps the next stream id
           └── it emits a CreateLinearStream event
